{"tid":2230731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白俄續有10萬人示威 要求釋放政治犯  警方發射水砲驅散","createTime":"2020-10-05T06:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T07:44:32.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d230637b3db2118435cffecddd7eb07b5a7cdd81","tid":2230731,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553018-20201005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553018-20201005.htm&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=600d9109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553018-20201005.htm&h=be6b4485\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553018-20201005.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1553018_1_20201005004008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1553018_1_20201005004008.jpg&h=7f397c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白俄羅斯首都明斯克再有大批民眾上街，要求當局釋放政治犯，反對派聲稱有10萬人參與，警方出動水砲車驅散，幾十人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n示威者響應反對派號召，當地星期日先在市中心聚集，再遊行到相信關押大批政治犯的拘留中心，沿途揮舞象徵反對派的紅白旗幟，他們再次表明拒絕承認8月的總統大選結果，要求總統盧卡申科下台，大批警員封鎖市中心多條道路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=407849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407849&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGGvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5be35c31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407849&h=84ff4484\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=407849</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】白俄羅斯連續第八個星期有民眾上街示威，要求總統盧卡申科下台。<br />\n<br />\n在首都明斯克，有超過十萬名民眾於市中心遊行，他們揮動象徵反對派的紅白間旗幟，及高舉反政府標語。警方出動水炮車驅散，但民眾未有完全散去，他們要求總統盧卡申科下台，及釋放所有政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n白俄羅斯自8月總統選舉後，民眾多次上街示威，拒絕承認執政26年的盧卡申科勝選，並要求他下台。當局至今拘押超過一萬名示威者，至少244人以不同罪名被控。"},{"pid":"5016e40cdcc1e427e25091a8b353b6532fc67e2c","tid":2230731,"uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb05dfee0bb4c44948d253a0ba612810ebdcfaec","tid":2230731,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"天下極權一樣黑<br />\n唔好再話乜警察<br />\n係個政權比權佢先夠膽做到咁"},{"pid":"ce31b6dd5cf79f4eadba0e69e3cd9616600c4a69","tid":2230731,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T07:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}